{"tid":549964,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"少女和60多歲阿公爺孫戀","createTime":"2018-02-04T08:47:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-25T18:51:42.000Z","uid":25345,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0e7da0b16b0b5115e77977d6cade7ebf9daef557","tid":549964,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T08:47:38.000Z","msg":"孫戀在現今社會不容易被人接受，最近在東南亞國家瘋傳一組爺孫戀自拍照片，尺度相當大，兩人擺出各種姿勢自拍，有些照片中少女只穿一件胸罩，和阿公男友在床邊拍照，這些照片引起網友瘋傳、熱議。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，這是菲律賓版的爺孫戀，男子年約60多歲，女方傳出還未成年，兩人的照片尺度很大，互動相當親密，照片中有多張兩人在床上相擁的照片，甚至阿公男友掐女方胸的畫面。<br />\n<br />\n這組照片在東南亞國家瘋傳，照片已有數千次分享，幾萬人按讚，也登上各國媒體。雖然菲版爺孫戀的自拍系列照沒有露點，但由於尺度太大，且女方疑似未成年，引起網友的憤怒。<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_php6wzngN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_php6wzngN.jpg&h=9fecd2c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpIKLI8l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpIKLI8l.jpg&h=68ad728c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpYb2wMZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpYb2wMZ.jpg&h=7aca2221&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5694efa6c8f7f1552c2803eff720786aa6d0dc73","tid":549964,"uid":8867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T08:49:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"db2e528b25c6056024d264b1d6f8939e4ef676a3","tid":549964,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T08:52:33.000Z","msg":"阿公男友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3231a241026f0a1fd8aed229d206d16bd309ae5","tid":549964,"uid":208935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T18:51:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}